# Privacy Policy
To the extent permitted by law, SimpleSpyware explicitly disclaims responsibility or liability for any damages, material or otherwise, resulting from access to the information it publishes, the use or non-use of that information, misuse of the online connection or technical deficiencies of any kind. SimpleSpyware has not checked any of the third-party websites or libraries (i.e. websites operating from a other domain name) linked to this app via hyperlinks, and can therefore assume no responsibility for their content or for any products and services offered on them.

This data protection notice provides an overview of how data are collected and processed on within SimpleSpyware app. The following information is intended to provide you with an overview of how your personal data are processed by us on our website and what your rights are under data protection law. How and which data are processed depends on the actual circumstances.

What sources and data do we use?
We do not process data that are generated or collected by the use of our app and/or data that are provided by you
(e.g. when using the app, completing online forms or other requests).

Your personal data in particular when you use the SimpleSpyware on your local phone is collected, but not shared with anyone. This app can and will collect personal data audio, photo, device information and location and or user behavior for demonstration and educational purposes.
